       </div>
                                   <p>The Shoprite Group of Companies, comprising several iconic brands, is the largest retailer in Africa. It started out as a group of eight grocery stores in 1979, and has grown into a technologically-advanced, continent-wide business selling items from food, liquor and medicine, to concert tickets and furniture. Today the Group is at the forefront of retail...  

        <br />
    <a href="/jobs-at/shoprite-group-of-companies" class="view-all2" style="margin-top:0px">Read more about this company</a>
        <p style="margin-bottom:0px;">&nbsp;</p>

        
    <ul class="table-of-content">
